VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT \bcookies\[[^\]]+\]\s*=\s*\{(?![^\}]*\b(?:secure|httponly)\b)
WHEN EXPR MISSING:secure:\s*true|httponly:\s*true|SameSite|HttpOnly && PRESENT:cookies\[.*\]\s*=\s*\{
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects cookie assignments without explicit secure and HttpOnly attributes.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Cookies Missing Secure or HttpOnly Flags.
